SIMPLE: unsighted
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsighted
<hw>Un*sight"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not sighted, or
seen.</def> <rj><au>Suckling.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Gun.)</fld> <def>Not aimed by means of a sight;
also, not furnished with a sight, or with a properly adjusted sight;
<as>as, to shoot and <ex>unsighted</ex> rife or cannon</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsignificant</ent>⟦br⟧
